        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure L 54. Labels. i Bulimus schmidti Pfeiffer, 1854 ii Bulimus scitulus Reeve, 1849 iii Otostomus scitus H. Adams, 1867 iv Bulimulus (Drymaeus) selli Preston, 1909 v Bulimus serotinus Morelet, 1860 vi Bulimus serratus Pfeiffer, 1855." , "Figure 41. Drymaeus species. A-C Drymaeus (Drymaeus) arcuatostriatus (Pfeiffer, 1855), lectotype NHMUK 1975455 (H = 27.6) D-F Drymaeus (Drymaeus) expansus (Pfeiffer, 1848), holotype of Otostomus scitus H. Adams, 1867 NHMUK 1867.5.18.5 (H = 27.1) G-I Drymaeus (Drymaeus) bartletti (H. Adams, 1867), lectotype NHMUK 1867.5.18.4 (H = 28.5). All enlarged." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26821" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26707" .

